originContent: # Foca: Cluster membership discovery on your terms

originContent: Foca is a building block for your gossip-based cluster discovery. It's
translatedContent: Foca es un componente para el descubrimiento de clústeres basado en gossip. Es

translatedContent: con sus extensiones útiles (`SWIM+Inf.+Susp.`).
